

	 
      The achievements which society rewards are won at the cost of diminution of personality  Divorce is a game played by lawyers.  Accomplishment is easiest when we work the hardest, and it is hardest when we work the easiest.  If your strength is small, don't carry heavy burdens. If your words are worthless, don't give advice.  In nature there are neither rewards nor punishments there are only consequences.  Some people never head a procession until they're dead.  Life's too short for chess.  I want to be all used up when I die.  A good man dies when a boy goes wrong.  All philosophy lies in two words, sustain and abstain.  Personal satisfaction is the most important ingredient of success.  The mere process of growing old together will make the slightest acquaintance seem a bosom friend.  Education is a method whereby one acquires a higher grade of prejudices.  To make oneself an object, to make oneself passive, is a very different thing from being a passive object.
     
    
